	Made by Torch  |  v3.0 — Full Rewrite
	─────────────────────────────────────────
	Bug fixes in this version:
	  [1]  Global scope leaks (Resizing/Resizeable) → local
	  [2]  Connect/Clone/Destroy wrong syntax → helper wrappers
	  [3]  Blur nil-crash on any button → nil-guard SafeBlur()
