	  [11] SetSetting "Theme" rejected tables → accepts string OR table
	  [12] Slider update loop uses task.wait (laggy) → RunService.RenderStepped
	  [13] AddTab duplicate error has no context → includes Tab name in error
	  [14] Color helper doesn't clamp → SafeRGB clamp 0-255
	  [15] MouseEnter/Leave not used for hover → added alongside InputBegan/Ended
	WindUI-style redesign:
	  - Gotham Bold/Semibold fonts throughout
	  - Accent-colored slider fill + toggle
